Package: UCSCTrackTools
Version: 2.2.0
Title: Tools to convert BAM files to BigWig and to create session track line
Author: Chao-Jen Wong
Maintainer: Chao-Jen Wong <cwon2@fhcrc.org>
Depends:  R (>= 3.3), GenomicRanges
Imports: RColorBrewer, biovizBase, GenomicAlignments, Rsamtools, BiocParallel, rtracklayer, GenomeInfoDb, SGSeq
Description: Tools to convert BAM files to bigWig files using coverage on genome
  positions. The session track line append the track lines for each bigWig file.
  Note that the preferred destinations for the coverage bigWig and junction bigBed files are
  /fh/fast/tapscott_s/pub/tapscott/ucsc/bigWig and /fh/fast/tapscott_s/pub/tapscott/ucsc/junction,
  respectively. The url portal is "http://tapscott:FSHD@xfiles.fhcrc.org:7007/ucsc/tapscott"
License: Artistic-2.0
LazyLoad: yes

